## Quantity Field

A numeric field paired with a unit, rendered with configurable formatting (decimals, unit suffix, min/max bounds).

### Usage

```ts
import { CardDef, field, contains } from 'https://cardstack.com/base/card-api';
import QuantityField from '@cardstack/catalog/fields/quantity/quantity';

export class Example extends CardDef {
  @field amount = contains(QuantityField, {
    configuration: { unit: 'kg', decimals: 2 },
  });
}
```

See the **Examples** section of this spec for the full set of supported configuration options.
